*intel-gpu-tools-1.11-r1 (11 Jul 2015)

  11 Jul 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +intel-gpu-tools-1.11-r1.ebuild,
  -intel-gpu-tools-1.11.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Add libunwind dependency. Fixes bug #554204. Patch by tka.

*intel-gpu-tools-1.11 (07 Jul 2015)

